os termales y los viajes, que reflejan una sensibilidad profunda hacia la tradición y la estética de su país.\n\nA día de hoy, sigue activa en la industria y continúa ampliando su trayectoria con nuevos proyectos. Entre sus trabajos más recientes destaca su participación en el drama Dear My Baby: Watashi ga Anata o Shihai suru made, donde interpretó a la madre del protagonista, reafirmando su presencia en papeles de fuerte carga emocional.","name":"Sayaka Yamaguchi","primary":false}}]}},"person_5437593_translations":{"at":1773688734858,"data":{"id":5437593,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"เกรซ ฮาร์เปอร์","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Grace Harper is an actress under Channel 7. She studied at Stamford International University. She was a contestant on \"7HD NEW STARS\" and made her acting debut in the tiktok series \"I'm Your Boyy.\"","name":"Grace Harper","primary":false}}]}},"tv_259140_credits":{"at":1773689199989,"data":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":68472,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Kappei Yamaguchi","original_name":"山口勝平","popularity":2.8598,"profile_path":"/mJyxKRZxLv9D7LH5KcNSkjSKYOB.jpg","character":"Ranma Saotome (voice)","credit_id":"66983943505f1ba9ef804a71","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":40325,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Megumi Hayashibara","original_name":"林原めぐみ","popularity":2.3294,"profile_path":"/qiCiLNGaJmwql2uBpjnkY5zX5T2.jpg","character":"Ranma (voice)","credit_id":"66983957dec3c1452b804a91","order":1},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":55662,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Noriko Hidaka","original_name":"日髙のり子","popularity":1.6899,"profile_path":"/43OuwsjqGf7JxpFpUvB75OdDDXQ.jpg","character":"Akane Tendo (voice)","credit_id":"6698395e7479465e512ab853","order":2}],"crew":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":225571,"known_for_department